{"tid":2013886,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"26歲馮姓黨衛軍涉盜竊5萬元失物明日提堂","createTime":"2020-05-12T15:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T15:23:58.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f201ab2c5071d85f5a9a7fb6a9284c5c67d020","tid":2013886,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:05:03.000Z","msg":"26歲男警涉盜竊失物明日提堂<br />\n12.05.2020 22:56<br />\n<br />\n一名警員涉嫌盜竊失物，明日在沙田裁判法院提堂。事發在去年2月，有人在機場拾獲一個內有約5萬元現金的銀包，交到機場報案中心，失主在一小時後前往報案中心認領財物，但接班的當值人員發現無相關紀錄，懷疑財物被盜。警方經調查，在翌日凌晨拘捕一名26歲姓馮的男警員，涉嫌不當處理失物。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，非常重視警員的操守，若干犯違法行為，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287080&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1287080%26csid%3D261_341&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmNeKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=fe2bb4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287080&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"33b35ed6be3812d43b959fb48df87c5bee7497c3","tid":2013886,"uid":60831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"一單偷竊案由發生到上庭要15個月時間咁耐??"},{"pid":"4d5839a0e81266e4f55d072b4f4427870e53c495","tid":2013886,"uid":339539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"反正衰左都係坐監 做咩唔跟反黑組學下野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b50f3b9a9954778e26227cd9872503f2131a60","tid":2013886,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:23:58.000Z","msg":"已訓斥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}